function sysCall_init() particle_def = sim.particle_spheres + sim.particle_respondable1to4 + sim.particle_particlerespondable;
o=sim.addParticleObject(particle_def,0.011,5000,nil,0,99999,{0,0.6,0.99},nil,nil,nil); h=sim.getObjectHandle("FilledCup") p=sim.getObjectPosition(h,-1) i=0 end
function sysCall_actuation() if (i<50) then sim.addParticleObjectItem(o,{p[1],p[2],p[3]+0.05,p[1],p[2],p[3]+0.05}) i=i+1 end end
